Priest- (4)
- Has the ability to pray for someone (even for people outside their team) every night.
- Once they have prayed for someone thrice, they will be protected from all attacks on them until it expires. (Protection expires if they are attacked.)
- Prayer is completed instantly. Has no cooldown on abilities. Target is informed if they were prayed for. Prayer Protection is Strong Protection.
- Respawns in 4 phases.
